Zurich Financial Plans Brazil Reinsurance Unit, IstoE Reports

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-06-18T16:00:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-18/zurich-financial-plans-brazil-reinsurance-unit-istoe-reports.html
Zurich Financial Services Group
plans to invest 100 million reais ($63 million) to start a
reinsurance unit in  Brazil ,  IstoE Dinheiro  magazine said, citing
Antonio Cassio dos Santos, head of Latin America operations.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 